{"tid":1253544,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[廣東歌推介]香港好耐冇出過咁高質嘅MV","createTime":"2019-06-23T15:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T07:01:35.000Z","uid":24112,"like":52,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c9c755a7dcfc7d4b16c7cb72591de821d9799f","tid":1253544,"uid":24112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iutLnx2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiutLnx2.png&h=15d03395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日睇完已經好想share<br />\n<br />\n成個MV好有故事性 睇得出導演好多位拍得好細緻。<br />\n例如：利用左黑房去代表男主角內心世界  （黑房會食煙 現實世界唔食煙）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外兩位個男主角都做得好好。睇到入邊佢哋兩個好多細微互動，真係比到人有個種兄弟情啊但有少少曖昧嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後相信無論係咩人都應該經歷過類似嘅經歷。想開口表白但係冇勇氣嘅嗰種心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完個MV個心拿住拿住，好多回憶重現返晒出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以首歌來講其實算係普通k唱 但係連埋個MV就成件事升華咗好多<br />\n<br />\n近年除咗juno來黎講 香港好似冇乜會令人有深刻印象嘅MV。希望嚟緊成個行業可以放多啲資源去拍MV <br />\n唔好淨係坐喺度行行企企歌手唱吓歌就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在錯誤的宇宙尋找愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2J_0nahRxBk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2J_0nahRxBk&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr14E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=5ba90f54\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2J_0nahRxBk</a>"},{"pid":"b93a12941a4b5271489f281ff9bcafad53f965bc","tid":1253544,"uid":24112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd36034021d4cb93cdc9a01ac7606003135c4683","tid":1253544,"uid":234261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor